name: Memoir 2021 #1
description:
This artwork was created with the help of AI built by NightCafe Studio.

In my 2021 year-end summary, I wrote:

> Many selves split into sections die one after another, by murder, suicide, or accident. One dies so another is forced to appear next as it is no one's fault coming with a new one - a delicate illusion supporting the flux of life and death. 

The AI turned this into an image.
